If you don't like the fact that you're paying more because you're driving 90 miles an hour

00:25:30.160 --> 00:25:37.040
down the highway, well, you can change your behavior and your price will adapt. And I think

00:25:37.040 --> 00:25:41.839
that is a satisfying realization for people as well. If you feel like you have control and you

00:25:41.839 --> 00:25:50.079
understand why you're paying what you are, there's sort of a feeling of justice with that, I think.

