That's, I think, a pretty fundamental requirement. We like people to have some experience in

00:49:26.000 --> 00:49:34.080
working with different data sets, whether it's just SQL experience or to have experience working

00:49:34.080 --> 00:49:41.520
in big data ecosystems, that would be great as well. Beyond that, I honestly, I think it's just

00:49:41.520 --> 00:49:48.320
