00:49:48.320 --> 00:49:56.479
problems in efficient ways. So even if you don't have five years of experience developing in Spark

00:49:56.479 --> 00:50:03.679
or Python, but you have some baseline knowledge of that and you're really eager and enthusiastic

00:50:03.679 --> 00:50:12.080
to learn and you've got a good sense about data and you're able to frame analytical questions well

