00:50:23.600 --> 00:50:31.520
do have some sort of advanced degree in some STEM related field and that could vary quite a bit,

00:50:31.520 --> 00:50:38.879
honestly. I think there are an increasing number of data analytics or data science

00:50:38.879 --> 00:50:43.600
programs at the master's level in particular, but we've also brought in some pretty

