Some of that varies by use case and you know frankly the capability and skill set of

00:53:41.840 --> 00:53:45.600
the teams that we're partnering with and some of them have you know pretty good analysts that are

00:53:45.600 --> 00:53:51.199
good at you know designing how we're going to measure the impact and they're able to drive

00:53:51.199 --> 00:53:56.639
some of that reporting independent of us. In some cases we have to take on more of that as well.

00:53:56.959 --> 00:54:04.399
So it really just kind of depends. For sure, laughing at the comments forever.

00:54:04.399 --> 00:54:09.120
I guess that's, it's ultimately a good measurement, right?

